Package apps.linear.postfix

Class Summary
PostfixDriver Postfix evaluation driver.
PostfixEvaluator This class evaluates a postfix expression.
StackKeeper This class implements a stack that is used to evaluate an expression, and stores floating point numbers.
StatusKeeper This class implements a status tracker that stores the portion of an expression that has been processed so far.
 

Enum Summary
PostfixDriver.Command List of commands that may be issued to the driver.
 

Exception Summary
IllegalExpressionException This class implements a checked exception that is thrown when an arithmetic expression is determined to be incorrectly structured.
